image_analysis.description: A wide-angle photograph of a large, commercial-style kitchen. The room features white cabinetry, stainless steel countertops and backsplashes, and a black and white checkered floor. There is a large professional-grade stove and oven unit under a massive stainless steel ventilation hood. A smaller dishwasher unit is integrated into the cabinetry on the left. A glass-topped table with two grey chairs is positioned in the center of the room. The ceiling is a drop-tile grid with recessed lighting and square light panels.
